value.string: To get the Horison Id of required partner and split the alphabets and Numbers.
1. Open the excel reference file, identify the Horison ID(Column C) based on the partner type in Column A for all the 10 partners.

2. Nine separate logics to split the alphanumeric number (Horison ID) into alphabets & numbers  for each partner by referring to an excel sheet and then incrementing the number by 1 for each unique Agency Name in the partner file.
3. In case of failure while Loading the file/entering to a field, ERROR flag will be raised and BOT may be stopped.
---------Comparing Partner Name with excel and get the corresponding Horison ID
